# Click any zone, watch every clip from it


```playwright
await fx.say("Every row on the right side is a bucket — by zone, shot type, contest level, quarter, opponent. One click and the player surfaces every clip from that bucket.");
await fx.cursorTo("button[aria-label='Watch Paint clips']");
await fx.pause(0.5);
await page.click("button[aria-label='Watch Paint clips']");
await page.waitForSelector("[role='dialog'][aria-label='Clip viewer']", { timeout: 8000 });
await fx.pause(4.5);
await page.locator("button[aria-label='Next clip']").click();
await fx.pause(3.5);
await page.keyboard.press("Escape");
await fx.pause(0.8);
```

